At the time you went into the front shop was there any muslin laid on the counter? - A. There was;
Mary Johnson
bargained, bought, and paid for some thread; the muslin was left in the back shop. on the counter.

Q. Was the lead cut? - A. No, it was ripped;
Joseph Williams
is my landlord, he is down at Salisbury, he has the lease of the house.
